{"tid":99812,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"（長）已經4年，對唔住，我同你講咗大話，最後放棄我","createTime":"2017-01-29T13:11:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T10:41:57.000Z","uid":75074,"like":9,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a59faa32a02ccd3ca0fe80f935f50ee622442b8c","tid":99812,"uid":75074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:11:51.000Z","msg":"事發4年前我同個男仔一齊咗，<br />\n<br />\n個男仔係個好重視誠信嘅人，由識佢到拍拖佢都講得好清楚，有咩事都一定一定要講真話，一定會包容，體諒，大家唔啱傾到啱。<br />\n<br />\n而我都事無大小都同佢講，坦誠相對。佢講過好多次點都唔會放棄我扔低我，除非我呃佢。<br />\n<br />\n佢全心全意對我，個世界只有我一個，我第一次覺得被愛嘅感覺係點。<br />\n<br />\n到分咗手先知原來呢個世界上真係好難再搵到一個對我咁好嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n事發係一齊咗一段時間後，傾開我同前男友嘅野。我就同佢講話我地好純，咩都無做過。<br />\n<br />\n佢仲叫佢一定要信我，發誓話點會呃佢個啲說話。賤到發脾氣幾日屈番佢唔信我。<br />\n<br />\n但其實。。我有幫ex含過，當時我好驚佢會覺得我係啲好求奇嘅女人，所以我竟然選擇咗呃佢。<br />\n<br />\n同埋我傻傻的以為我ex一定唔會亂講出去，同埋個男仔一定一定唔會識佢。（我仲專登whatsapp佢叫佢守秘密，唉）<br />\n<br />\n點不知過多咗幾個月，個男仔竟然知道咗。我ex有次飲酒，醉醉地同佢個男姓朋友講咗，誰不知個男仔轉折下竟然知道咗呢樣野。（我諗都無諗過。。）<br />\n<br />\n之後佢就約我出黎講清楚，話唔明點解我要咁做。佢接受到我幫人含，但接受唔到我呃佢。再重覆問我記唔記得佢最在意嘅係誠信。。我知佢當時仲好愛我，佢雙眼通紅嘅畫面咁多年黎依然係我腦海揮之不去。<br />\n<br />\n最後我地都係分咗手，佢好決絕，我有諗過佢其實係咪介意件事，我主動話幫番佢，甚至話可以俾佢掂，但佢都拒絕，話最在乎嘅係我地之間坦誠嘅相處。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新一年，上黎發洩下，希望有心愛嘅人嘅你地好好珍惜對方，唔好有隱瞞，即使係啲你認為無可能會拆穿嘅謊言。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後：<br />\n你真係一個好好嘅男仔，對唔住，傷害咗你，到宜家我都好內疚，好後悔。個晚嘅情節依然揮之不去。如果你有緣睇到嘅，可唔可以搵番我。。只想親口同你講對唔住<br />\n<br />\n希望你新一年開開心心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"912986516799cccf5c7d5584e73a3b4a028ad8b2","tid":99812,"uid":29148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:15:12.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"711673be5bc63c006c7db2b486836d1fc8366942","tid":99812,"uid":75074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:16:23.000Z","msg":"襯佢仲俾機會你時你要好好珍惜。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n建立信任要好長時間，摧毁只需一秒。。"},{"pid":"7c38428e1bb9d7535390924cbb924472c866532c","tid":99812,"uid":71319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:21:25.000Z","msg":"誠信真係好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1484bafff2fa4d71cda53a3a13292c5daed1e3a","tid":99812,"uid":8833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:26:10.000Z","msg":"係 坦白好緊要<br />\n但試問邊個會無自己祕密<br />\n<br />\n對你地表示可惜"},{"pid":"20b865ce52dbf6743c6bb07bbbef04a908969dbf","tid":99812,"uid":75074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:26:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>誠信真係好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無咗嘅話真係講咩都無用"},{"pid":"3353040f755666d333c6a7c08052a2e52f6184ac","tid":99812,"uid":75074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:31:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係 坦白好緊要<br />\n但試問邊個會無自己祕密<br />\n<br />\n對你地表示可惜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗要分輕重<br />\n同埋佢自己本身就對我好坦白"},{"pid":"83cf4dfbf856a1dfacefa3fd2d4cc6da31f9ff51","tid":99812,"uid":14392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:32:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb1ca10dcc50a157c4fdfc6079e7f034f930458a","tid":99812,"uid":9006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:38:59.000Z","msg":"自作自受,抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d874e6c4d278a6b8e9b926e39ab7361976c6d420","tid":99812,"uid":8000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:41:37.000Z","msg":"含點解又唔講得<br />\n一定唔止啦"},{"pid":"29c6a9e972aeb7c8a30eb9c64cc8916f415f544f","tid":99812,"uid":29506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:50:57.000Z","msg":"贈二字： 抵死"},{"pid":"4818f5c7247214a2121c1145e670658a25b1e632","tid":99812,"uid":49228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:58:57.000Z","msg":"點解你要講大話啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82b8b71932947b006aa3090443d1e90e4dd88ca","tid":99812,"uid":75074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T14:00:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自作自受,抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係"},{"pid":"a234f0154fbc21075ce66a0b87bf894c2acece9b","tid":99812,"uid":75074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T14:00:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解你要講大話啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一時諗唔開。。唉"},{"pid":"ad517e6bfe5b3d86f1a7cc5ccf8e7740c5e559ec","tid":99812,"uid":67126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T14:06:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"12ebea7774d32f7fbff9f9c86bbf2111f0d394be","tid":99812,"uid":3712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T14:09:02.000Z","msg":"滿口謊言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5df0fc2c27fc8639e3947feb218c50f1bb36454","tid":99812,"uid":40980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T14:14:09.000Z","msg":"傳到到條仔到，姐係話好多人都知，條仔仲點見人<br />\n<br />\n你怪就怪有個𡁻完唱嘅ex，當然你唔老實都係抵死嫁啦"},{"pid":"3114a11f9420c48db77d6402cf2af03b83d3d7f5","tid":99812,"uid":11230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T14:15:31.000Z","msg":"佢對你咁好<br />\n點解你又要咁對佢呢?<br />\n將心比已"},{"pid":"b35f4e05d6c55798a8030711c25d5b648ccd18f9","tid":99812,"uid":21569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T14:20:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係 坦白好緊要<br />\n但試問邊個會無自己祕密<br />\n<br />\n對你地表示可惜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗要分輕重<br />\n同埋佢自己本身就對我好坦白</blockquote><br />\n可能佢都有呢"},{"pid":"49b4ead1e6a04c5b1fd31f16b7227762f5bf3527","tid":99812,"uid":75074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T14:44:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>滿口謊言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對唔住"},{"pid":"fc39364a34e4cc601c38cd8ce98378be56bd126c","tid":99812,"uid":75074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:27:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢對你咁好<br />\n點解你又要咁對佢呢?<br />\n將心比已</blockquote><br />\n我個時真係諗唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5bb3838a4ea26ccd0cf13b028109ba942ee796","tid":99812,"uid":75074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T17:02:40.000Z","msg":"Where are you now"},{"pid":"40e04a1c6e993b851c29f38bfb4be5b567017261","tid":99812,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T17:39:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Where are you now</blockquote><br />\n重視誠信嘅男仔都好少有。"},{"pid":"558eec3c9b905e695b0bc918bcf9e520d36f2741","tid":99812,"uid":44883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T18:25:50.000Z","msg":"雖然同樓主經歷不同<br />\n但希望我ex 都會好似樓主咁諗起我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n那晚的影像 還在我海中揮之不去<br />\n不知你有沒有<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0279983dd362d91c41576ffe0ffb961b75124fca","tid":99812,"uid":16935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T19:33:26.000Z","msg":"毒撚真係好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 利申：死毒撚"},{"pid":"f4815f8218f84053df61fb11370a9677d6a54d31","tid":99812,"uid":16935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T19:38:50.000Z","msg":"四年後俾幾多條仔屌過啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44043bfc4139a22de117a150939d203ecaa3f422","tid":99812,"uid":27772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T19:51:40.000Z","msg":"其實你冇問題 <br />\n只係根本唔夾 <br />\n咁既人一齊會好大壓力"},{"pid":"4b4241a4fe4a130a0e0b83b3f6a224a0d2f75e06","tid":99812,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T19:59:37.000Z","msg":"橙，又一隻g"},{"pid":"4bbd9d7aec4f317a1acb669c8e24c53eb919a60b","tid":99812,"uid":75074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:20:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Where are you now</blockquote><br />\n重視誠信嘅男仔都好少有。</blockquote><br />\n我都覺<br />\n自此之後都無遇過<br />\n曾經有啲睇落以為幾好嘅<br />\n但都瞞口謊言 偷偷地撩其他女仔<br />\n<br />\n但我自己當時又可嘗唔係滿口謊言"},{"pid":"858dff4378b5c393d6a49c517101ef2db5e91ed0","tid":99812,"uid":75074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:21:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>四年後俾幾多條仔屌過啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無sorry"},{"pid":"f63be6d323a7b524a8558b92ec4c9de407493bdb","tid":99812,"uid":11461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:23:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a9d564b0f688cef497de2f5eeade18a7bc1aa27e","tid":99812,"uid":10612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:29:18.000Z","msg":"誠信岩阿 抵你比人飛<br />\n所以我唔會信女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nEx話同人扑過一次 我問佢係咪10個男人內 佢話係就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd2b3226e2824d84408557b2ebd04e259e98046b","tid":99812,"uid":69425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:30:58.000Z","msg":"我覺得好小事咋喎，每個人都一定有啲小秘密，而且都係善意嘅大話，佢咁小嘢都咁執著，點做人呀，你同佢一齊都大壓力啦！"},{"pid":"60de58abafece4ef4e9078a18c7917b4b22f35e5","tid":99812,"uid":75074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:32:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本21世紀 男人唔介意你有冇同人做過愛<br />\n最緊要坦白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過你呃人自己落黎賤<br />\n<br />\n我EXEX都呃過我 發現左之後都KEEP住拍拖兩年幾. 但一直有條刺</blockquote><br />\n同意<br />\n只要我當時坦白同佢講 佢就會無野<br />\n所以我到宜家都好後悔"},{"pid":"21dfdd7eea97328ecd780982382fb804f51ac2aa","tid":99812,"uid":75074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:36:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得好小事咋喎，每個人都一定有啲小秘密，而且都係善意嘅大話，佢咁小嘢都咁執著，點做人呀，你同佢一齊都大壓力啦！</blockquote><br />\n我諗佢介意嘅一點係我當時口口聲聲話自己無 仲發番佢脾氣轉頭話佢<br />\n分手後佢同我講番話開始分唔到我邊句真邊句假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f973432f7db58a130f69124b5a4865bc320b10f5","tid":99812,"uid":75074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:42:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然同樓主經歷不同<br />\n但希望我ex 都會好似樓主咁諗起我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n那晚的影像 還在我海中揮之不去<br />\n不知你有沒有<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你因為佢呃你所以飛佢？<br />\n而你仲未放低佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6ae5d74554804e829227a212afa4468b95303a","tid":99812,"uid":76678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:52:55.000Z","msg":"自我反省，吸取教訓，下次(個)做好"},{"pid":"71a4153246f1a338a677348fa589f07d03f07887","tid":99812,"uid":70182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:56:42.000Z","msg":"真係一係唔好講，一講就講真。<br />\n你男友應該係d好敏感既人，可以好易知道你有沒有講大話。所以好討厭人地向佢面前講大話果種虛假感。<br />\n而且你講左一次，佢次次都要懷疑你就會好辛苦。"},{"pid":"a15e65d2cce18d341f70aa0af3401b708f6629f3","tid":99812,"uid":28590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T04:01:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係一係唔好講，一講就講真。<br />\n你男友應該係d好敏感既人，可以好易知道你有沒有講大話。所以好討厭人地向佢面前講大話果種虛假感。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而且你講左一次，佢次次都要懷疑你就會好辛苦。</span></blockquote><br />\n同意，而且唔係一方。雙方都好辛苦"},{"pid":"4188b6b81f5e4bc2a44d2879b2e6f1eda39620df","tid":99812,"uid":45188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T04:06:44.000Z","msg":"誠信真係好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f20b7919aafe5102af63377aba514b66eab8ce","tid":99812,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T04:16:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f7165c356e27628aecb2c32080