By":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T05:07:10.000Z","msg":"[size=5][/si<span style=\"color: red;\">樓主係雞係公廁，抵撚死</span>ze=5]"},{"pid":"3551707e1a9402a34cdca9519a1e7b42ec5b79af","tid":99812,"uid":63490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T06:00:47.000Z","msg":"體諒樓主既 因為有啲野真係好難開口 不過如果我係你既話我會選擇遲啲講好過呃佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />尤其是呢種男仔咁有原則 真係一次不忠百次不用"},{"pid":"371207708342fbd1e66eaba685450eed698c65a0","tid":99812,"uid":56214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T07:48:23.000Z","msg":"我好重誠信，求PM <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96cdabc3ef567294d2660517c2d9c3d3be0fc32d","tid":99812,"uid":57226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T07:51:47.000Z","msg":"仲要話用口幫返佢 你真係on9"},{"pid":"2e92b5b933bc1359cb13a6699d4781e81901472c","tid":99812,"uid":7524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T07:53:14.000Z","msg":"講明坦白都要講大話，抵死<br />\n<br />\n上一段都係衰呢樣"},{"pid":"c004e84a21e1ac385e06adfd7cc970f0aa41e15e","tid":99812,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:47:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我好重誠信，求PM <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n&hellip;"},{"pid":"387d990bcac0d876da3458a59560c96a594fb8f9","tid":99812,"uid":75074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:46:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講明坦白都要講大話，抵死<br />\n<br />\n上一段都係衰呢樣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果佢無講明坦白嘅可能都罪不至此<br />\n<br />\n所以我無怪過佢 只怪自己"},{"pid":"47a2d6c25c09c097b185fe9e88cb6f958334db77","tid":99812,"uid":75074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:47:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲要話用口幫返佢 你真係on9</blockquote><br />\n我以為佢係介意呢件事嘛 點知原來佢唔care<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  最care 係我聲大夾惡呃佢"},{"pid":"e01a5d46a890cec19790b4bef4fe8b4651caa8ee","tid":99812,"uid":75589,"like":0,"di